@startuml sequence_realtime
!theme plain
title SignalR Connection + Team Broadcast

actor "User A" as A
actor "User B" as B
participant "RealtimeService(A)" as RA
participant "TeamHub" as Hub
participant "RealtimeService(B)" as RB
participant "Handler(some mutator)" as H

A -> RA: connect()
RA -> Hub: connect (cookie auth)
Hub -> Hub: AddToGroupAsync team:{teamId}
RA --> A: connected

B -> RB: connect()
RB -> Hub: connect
Hub -> Hub: AddToGroupAsync team:{teamId}

== A creates a contact ==
A -> H: POST /api/contacts
H -> Hub: Group(team).SendAsync("contactCreated", {eventType, entityId, actorId, timestamp, data})
Hub --> RA: contactCreated envelope (echo)
Hub --> RB: contactCreated envelope
RB --> B: notify subscribers

== A signs out ==
A -> RA: disconnect()
RA -> Hub: stop
@enduml
